CatDescriptText: Small wooden church with cement block foundation on a dirt road.  A small cross on the roof peak is the only sign of its purpose.  A cornerstone near the door is illegible.  Residential homes surround the church at left and right.  Power and phone lines on wooden poles line the streets.
TitMainTitle: St. Mark AME Zion Church at intersection of dirt roads Western Avenue, Old Hill Road, and Division Street, Jeannette, Pennsylvania
